                    (SFA), 5600
                    <emph type="italic">i</emph>
                    (SBA) and 5900
                    <emph type="italic">i</emph>
                    (SFA) with Tilt Hood
                </caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. CENTER HOOD GUIDE</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. HEX BOLT</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </svcsubproc>
